data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom brick 1.5 story house. This home offers  1st floor utility/laundry room, Nice size 1st floor bath. Large 2nd floor bath. Approx 24 ft deep x 24 ft wide concrete block garage.  Fenced back yard with open field behind the property line. There is a brand new roof installed on 2022. The water heater installed in 2020 and new floors added 2021 in the office.
